epd_container¶

namespace EPD¶

A collection of use-case filters, namely for parsing usecase_config.txt, Counting and Color-Matching usecaseMode.

class EPDContainer¶
#include <epd_container.hpp>

An Easy Perception Deployment(EPD) Container class object. The EPDContainer class object parses the session_config.txt and usecase_config.txt files to determine how an ONNX model can be deployed as an inference engine using the ONNXRuntime library.

The filepath to the essential class label list, that maps classIndices to human-understandable object text labels.

The filepath to an input ONNX model file.

The selected use-case mode. Values can only be 0,1,2.

See usecase_config.hpp for more details.
